cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is about machine learning and specifically focuses on data selection using a deep reinforcement learning framework. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions applications in image classification (cs.CV) and text understanding (cs.CL), which further supports these categories. Additionally, the use of deep neural networks suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as a likely category. Finally, the use of reinforcement learning suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category.
